commit_message:
Use senlin generic driver to manege keystone driver

Several jobs were done in this patch:
1. Enable keystone driver plugin;
2. Minor revise the implementation of driver plugin to enable the
   invoking of classmethod;
3. Invoke context.get_service_context rather than get_serice_credential
   defined in driver layer to get service user credential;

Change-Id: I612413ce36c59ff33a15b2d24aaf1c07c47447a1
Partially implement: blueprint reimplement-senlin-drivers-as-plugin

[Ref Arch] Rephrase router gateway IP description

This patch:
- adds a description of router gateway IP while adding a new router;
- adds pictures that show new router gateway selection;
- adds a reference to the Configuring the network diagram;
- adds the router network IP 12.0.0.1/24 as example to the diagram
  description.

Change-Id: I867cb13b4049b9a27d551170f3152231c499f09c
Closes-Bug: #1421544
